media:group.media:title: Why Inclusion Matters - Episode 3
media:group.media:description:
Here's Episode 3 of Netflix's Series "Why Inclusion Matters" where Meghana Bhatt, Bao Ngo and Omair Akhtar discuss building inclusive teams!
“I want somebody that’s not like anybody on the team because that additivity is just, it’s magic!” - Bao Ngo
